This project is the production QA evaluation platform for the Flickerflash DGAF ecosystem, featuring:
- Agent Apogee evidence governance — Phase 1-4 source validation and multi-phase review
- Agent Amethyst meta-orchestration and Gold Star certification authority
- Agent Sentinel CI/CD integrity enforcement and guardrail activation
- DGAF (Dynamic Governance Agentic Formation Framework) compliance alignment
- NIST AI Risk Management Framework (AI RMF) evaluation protocols
- OWASP Agentic Top 10 safety sweep integration
- Rose Gold Submission framework and evidence scoring rubrics
- Benchmark evaluation suite with multi-dimensional scoring

Governance spine: https://github.com/Flickerflash/DGAF-Framework
Agent Roster: https://github.com/Flickerflash/DGAF-Framework/blob/main/ENSEMBLE_ROSTER.md

Designed for institutional and enterprise evaluation of AI system governance compliance.
